
steps:

1. File > New Project > Console Application.
2. Give a name "server controls"
3.Go to Pages Folder > index.cshtml

4. Code for index.cshtml :
@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Homepage";
}

<div>
    <img src="~/images/amity-logo.jpg" alt="Amity University Logo" style="max-width: 200px;" />
</div>

<nav style="margin-top: 20px;">
    <ul style="list-style: none; display: flex; gap: 20px; padding: 0;">
        <li><a asp-page="/GridviewDemo">Gridview Demo</a></li>
        <li><a asp-page="/LinqDemo">LINQ Demo</a></li>
        <li><a asp-page="/Login">Login</a></li>
    </ul>
</nav>

5. Go to wwwroot folder > Right click > make new folder and name it add "Images" 
6. Right click on Images folder > Add > Exsisting File  > select "amity-logo.jpg" 
